text: Rachael Leigh Cook (born October 4, 1979) is an American actress, model and voice artist. She played Becky Thatcher in Tom and Huck (1995). She played Laney Boggs in She's All That (1999). She played Laura King in the movie Vampire (2011). She was born in Minneapolis, Minnesota. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:Actors from Minneapolis Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:1979 births Category:Living people
